.modal.hide.fade
  .modal-header
    h3 Awaiting other party...
  
  .modal-body
    :markdown
      Please provide the following URL to the other party for confirmation of the terms.
      This page will be updated automatically when the other party agrees to proceed.

      Closing this page will cancel the transaction.

    pre.url.click-to-select= alice_url

    .muted
      :markdown
        This URL contains your *public* key, the arbitrator public key, the terms and your digital
        signature of the terms.

  .modal-footer
    button.btn(data-dismiss='modal') Cancel transaction

